      The Glenn Beck Program - 1/2/14Thursday, January 02, 2014 10:42 AM


Doc and Skip fill in for Glenn and they kick off an interesting debate about contraception.

  Since the Federal Government wants contraceptives covered under Obamacare,

   Doc says all sexual acts and accessories also need to be covered...you're going to want to hear this.

  Also, Bill Deblasio was sworn in as the new mayor of NYC 
      and he's looking to make major changes and proclaimed progressivism is coming to NYC.



  Plus, 40,000 new laws were passed in 2013 and pretty much each is more ridiculous than the next.
